# Scopes the build context for deploy/cloudflare/Dockerfile (the only Docker
# build in this repo — context is the repo root, see wrangler.jsonc
# image_build_context). Whitelist just what the image COPYies so wrangler
# deploy doesn't ship node_modules/.venv/frontend builds to the Docker daemon.
*
!backend/
!demo_app.py
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
